          Recevez des conseils sur le marketing digital par email toutes les 2
          semaines
        </h2>
        <Newsletter />
        <ul role="list" class="social-links">
          <li>
            <a
              href="https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=61578725257899"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
            >
              <Icon name="facebook" title="Nous suivre sur Facebook" />
            </a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/malinsdeaudouce"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
            >
              <Icon name="linkedIn" title="Nous suivre sur Linkedin" />
            </a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              href="https://x.com/malinsdeaudouce"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
            >
              <Icon name="x" title="Nous suivre sur X" />
            </a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              href="https://www.youtube.com/@malinsdeaudouce"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
            >
              <Icon name="youtube" title="Nous suivre sur Youtube" />
            </a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h2 class="h4">Parcourir</h2>
        <Nav />
      </div>
      <div>
        <h2 class="h4">A propos</h2>
        <address>
          <a href="tel:0649886838">06 49 88 68 38</a>
          <br />
          <a href="mailto:contact@webro.fr">contact@webro.fr</a>
          <br />
          <a href="/contact">Envoyez un message</a>
          <br />
          Ouvert du lundi au vendredi de 10h à 18h
          <br />
          Basé dans les Vosges, Grand Est
        </address>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="container bg-black-dark">
    <ul role="list" class="footer__bottom">
      <li>
        <a href="/politique-de-confidentialite">Politique de confidentialité</a>
      </li>
      <li><a href="/sitemap-0.xml">Plan du site</a></li>
      <li>&copy; {currentYear} Malins d'eau douce</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  a {
    color: var(--accent);
    transition: color 0.3s;
    font-weight: 700;

    &:hover {
      color: var(--white);
    }
  }

  @media (width > 48rem) {
    footer {
      margin-top: 0.625rem;
    }
  }

  @media (width > 64rem) {
    footer {
      margin-top: 1.25rem;
    }
  }

  .footer__top {
    display: grid;
    align-items: start;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    padding: clamp(2.5rem, 1.875rem + 3.125vw, 5rem) 0;
    gap: clamp(2.5rem, 1.875rem + 3.125vw, 5rem) 1.25rem;

    > div {
      display: grid;
      justify-items: center;
      text-align: center;
      gap: 1.25rem;
    }

    .social-links {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 2.5rem;

      [data-icon] {
        width: 2rem;
        height: 2rem;
        transition: color 0.3s;
        color: var(--white);

        &:hover {
          color: var(--accent);
        }
      }
    }
  }

  .footer__bottom {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  @media (width > 48rem) {
    .bg-black {
      border-radius: 4px 4px 0 0;
    }
    .bg-black-dark {
      border-radius: 0 0 4px 4px;
    }
  }

  @media (width > 64rem) {
    .footer__top {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);

      > div {
        justify-items: start;
        text-align: start;

        &:first-child {
          grid-column: 1/3;
        }

        &:last-child {
          grid-column: 4/6;
        }
      }
    }

    .footer__bottom {
      flex-direction: row;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 1.25rem;
      gap: 0.625rem;

      li a {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.625rem;

        &::after {
          content: "";
          width: 4px;
          height: 4px;
          background-color: var(--white);
          border-radius: 2px;
        }
      }
    }
  }
</style>
